name: Allegany County Health Department
tweet: COVID-19 VACCINE WALK-IN WEDNESDAY!  Allegany Co. Fairgrounds, 11400 Moss Avenue, Cumberland, MD from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m.   No appointment needed for 1st, 2nd, or booster Pfizer dose (12+) or 1st or 2nd Moderna (18+).  (Appt. required for Moderna booster:    https://t.co/qrujhEZoMn.)
